text: Other Ocean Interactive is a video game developer from Emeryville, California. The company has worked with Mojang AB since 2017. The company started in California in 2006. It has made eight video games itself, and it has made 40 other video games. == Games == Other Ocean Interactive have made these video games itself: * Giant Cop: Justice Above All (PC) (2016) * #IDARB (Xbox One) (2015) * Puffins: Let's Race! (Nintendo DS) (2010) * Puffins: Let's Fish! (Nintendo DS) (2010) * Puffins: Let's Roll! (Nintendo DS) (2010) * Castlevania: Symphony of the Night (Xbox 360) (2007) They have also worked on these video games: * Yu-Gi-Oh! Legacy of the Duelist (PC, Xbox One, PlayStation 4) (2015) * Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Generationen (iPad, iPhone, Android) (2014) * Yu-Gi-Oh! Millennium Duels (Xbox 360, PlayStation 3) (2014) * NBA Rush (iPhone, iPad) (2014) * Gunstringer: Dead Man Running (PC) (2013) * Poptropica Adventures (Nintendo DS) (2012) * The Amazing Spider-Man (Xbox 360, PlayStation 3, Wii, Nintendo DS, PC, Nintendo 3DS, Wii U) (2012) * Minecraft: New Nintendo 3DS Edition (Nintendo 3DS) (2017) == References == == Other websites == * Other Ocean Interactive Category:Companies based in California Category:2006 establishments in the United States
title: Other Ocean Interactive
